---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { info } from "../data/info";
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
---

<BaseLayout title="About">
  <main class="max-w-2xl mx-auto px-4 py-16 sm:py-24">

    <header class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="space-y-4 order-2 sm:order-1">
        <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent">
          About
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-text dark:text-dk-text leading-relaxed">
          <strong>{info.name}</strong> is a
          full-stack engineer with a background in <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Business_intelligence">business intelligence</a> and <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Economics">economics</a>. He helps businesses turn complex data and
          processes into solutions that drive results.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="order-1 sm:order-2 shrink-0">
        <Image
          src={info.picture}
          alt={info.picture_alt}
          width={96}
          height={96}
          class="h-24 w-24 rounded-full object-cover grayscale contrast-115 shadow-sm border border-text/10 dark:border-dk-text/10"
        />
      </div>
    </header>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-text/90 dark:text-dk-text/90 leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        His professional journey began in BI, making data accessible through
        dashboards, automated reporting systems, and academic insights. 
        <br><br>
        Over
        time this evolved into building enterprise software that streamlines
        operations, increases efficiency, and supports strategic
        decision-making.
      </p>
      <p>
         His
        work primarily focuses on <strong>Elixir, .NET, Go, and JavaScript</strong>,
        while also exploring <strong>TypeScript, C, and Lua</strong> to build
        innovative, scalable solutions.
      </p>
      <p>
        Nick holds a bachelor's degree in economics and philosophy. This combines
        analytical thinking with technical expertise to deliver software that
        works.
      </p>

      <section class="pt-6">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-secondary dark:text-dk-accent mb-4">
          Personal Interests
        </h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-text/80 dark:text-dk-text/80">
          <li>Writing on <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/posts">his blog</a> 📝</li>
          <li>Football, the good kind ⚽</li>
          <li>Hanging out with his dog, <a class="text-dk-text underline" href="/bruce-the-dog">Bruce</a> 🐕</li>
          <li>Exploring trends in technology, business, and economics 📈</li>
          <li>Video games 🎮</li>
          <li>Experimenting with new programming languages and frameworks 🛠️</li>
          <li>Traveling ✈️</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
    </div>

    <footer class="mt-16 pt-8 border-t border-text/10 dark:border-dk-text/10">
      <a
        href="/"
        class="text-sm text-text/60 dark:text-dk-text/60 hover:text-secondary dark:hover:text-dk-accent transition-colors"
      >
        ← Back to home
      </a>
    </footer>

  </main>
</BaseLayout>